# Verify M10.4-1 — CH Buffer tables + config
# Date: 2026-05-27
# Acceptance: md_ticks_buffer/md_bars_buffer use Buffer engine + env-configurable params

## Buffer Table Verification

$ docker exec ant-clickhouse clickhouse-client --query "SELECT engine FROM system.tables WHERE database='ant' AND name='md_ticks_buffer'"
Buffer

$ docker exec ant-clickhouse clickhouse-client --query "SELECT engine FROM system.tables WHERE database='ant' AND name='md_bars_buffer'"
Buffer

## Buffer Config in clickhouse_writer.go

    FlushInterval time.Duration // 默认 500ms
    MaxBatchSize  int           // 默认 10000
    QueueSize     int           // 默认 50000；满则走 spill

Default values confirmed:
    FlushInterval: 500 * time.Millisecond,
    MaxBatchSize:  10000,
    QueueSize:     50000,

ENV override: ANT_CH_BUFFER_QUEUE_SIZE, ANT_CH_BUFFER_MAX_BATCH, ANT_CH_BUFFER_FLUSH_MS

## md_ticks sorting_key (ADR-0008 §2.2 compliant)
$ docker exec ant-clickhouse clickhouse-client --query "SELECT sorting_key FROM system.tables WHERE database='ant' AND name='md_ticks'"
broker, canonical, ts_unix_ms, bid, ask, bid_volume, ask_volume

